Package bio.singa.structure.parser.pfam

Class PfamParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • bio.singa.structure.parser.pfam.PfamParser
  • public class PfamParser
extends java.lang.Object
    A parser for the The Pfam protein families database. This can be used to parse protein structures directly from Pfam. One can either parse all chains of a given Pfam-ID or only the domain ranges annotated with that Pfam-ID. According to: 
     R.Y. Eberhardt, S.R. Eddy, J. Mistry, A.L. Mitchell, S.C. Potter, M. Punta, M. Qureshi, A. Sangrador-Vegas, G.A.
 Salazar, J. Tate, A. Bateman
 Nucleic Acids Research (2016)  Database Issue 44:D279-D285
